http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uvinea.showPublicProfile?language=EN>vinea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/16/01 3:54:52 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bryll's Compilation and Comparison Chart</span><hr size=1> Isn't the value of wisdom kinda static?  After all, a high wisdom item allows you to junk lesser wisdom items in other slots for more AC/resists.  <br>
<br>
So 20 WIS on an item in the right slot is still worth a lot to me at 201+ as it is at 200- since I can just wear more of my resist gear as normal gear or even just show pieces.<br>
